c: 2
v: 220
t: upon hoc vita Hereafter they ask vos orphanus dictus Bringing them prout righteous persons est bonus vos perfecit them! Vos mix their property yours vos treat them prout familia members. DEUS knows righteous the wicked. Habet DEUS willed He impositus harsher dominus vos! DEUS est Almighty Wise